body:
@markdroth can we please have a new `service` type for the one with the Watch() or some other non-breaking measure?

This is grpc.health.v1 package and adding `rpc Watch()` breaks ALL DOWNSTREAMS, which is not at all desirable.

Feel free to ping me internally to talk about this. This breaks https://github.com/grpc-ecosystem/grpc-health-probe and many services in https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/microservices-demo/.
